headline: The Confidence Paradox: 2025 Global Retirement Pulse Survey
summary: NEWARK, N.J., October 27, 2025--A new study by Prudential Financial, Inc. (NYSE: PRU) shows that mass affluent people around the world are confident about their retirement preparedness, but there is work to be done to help them protect their nest eggs and secure dependable income that lasts a lifetime.

headline: Why Analysts See a Changing Story for Prudential as Confidence Rises and Risks Remain
summary: Prudential’s Fair Value Estimate has seen a slight increase, rising from £11.998 to £12.03. Analysts are reassessing the company’s growth trajectory, and the change reflects a mix of optimism and measured caution. Improved revenue forecasts and recent business trends are driving the upward revision. Stay tuned to discover how investors can keep track of further changes in Prudential’s evolving story.
